				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Family BASIC exemplifies mapper 0 with WRAM. It was originally distributed with 2K or 4K of WRAM, but the decoding would be the same for 8K, which is what emulators typically implement.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

